<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of The China Syndrome, about a reporter who uncovers an accident at a nuclear power plant, and the plant officials who will stop at nothing to keep the truth covered up. Included are interviews with the cast and crew who share their experiences from making the film, as well as disscuss the efforts that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574120</url></doc>
